title: [Khystra's Weaponry]
[Khystra's Outfitting]
description: Blue watered silk walls rise from a glossy mahogany floor.  Just above a thick off-white carpet hangs a pearl-handled filigreed mandolin, and a mosaic tiled ceiling completes the picture.  A vine-carved mahogany table and a bamboo rack stand side by side in the middle of the room.
